This document tracks the refactoring roadmap for **my-app**. Prioritize items by impact and dependency.

---

## 🎯 High Priority

- [ ] Remove dead code and unused dependencies
- [ ] Eliminate \`any\` types; replace with strict TypeScript interfaces
- [ ] Break down files over 200 lines into smaller modules
- [ ] Replace \`any\` / \`as\` casts with proper type guards
- [ ] Extract shared logic into reusable hooks or utilities


---

## ⚡ Medium Priority

- [ ] Reduce deep nesting (max 3 levels of indentation)
- [ ] Name complex boolean logic with intention-revealing variables
- [ ] Align code style with project linting rules
- [ ] Replace magic numbers / strings with named constants
- [ ] Audit \`console.log\` calls; route through a proper logger
- [ ] Add deprecation notices with scheduled removal milestones

### Data Layer

- [ ] Extract inline data logic into typed repository functions

---

## 🧹 Low Priority

- [ ] Add JSDoc / TSDoc to all public API exports
- [ ] Improve test coverage on untested branches
- [ ] Split large test files into focused test suites
- [ ] Audit and update out-of-date inline comments
- [ ] Standardize import ordering with auto-fixable lint rules
- [ ] Reduce bundle size — tree-shake unused exports

---

## 📋 Progress

| Area | Status |
| :--- | :--- |
| **TypeScript strictness** | ⬜ Not started |
| **Dead code removal** | ⬜ Not started |
| **Error handling** | ⬜ Not started |
