This document details the high-level architecture, data flows, and design decisions for the **my-mern-app** project.

---

## 🏛️ System Overview

The system is configured as follows:
- **Frontend Layer**: \`React + Vite\`
- **Backend / Integration Layer**: \`Express\`
- **Database Layer**: \`MongoDB\`
