## 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Target Audience

- **Primary users**: Developers building Next.js applications
- **Secondary users**: AI agents operating on the codebase

---

## 🚀 Goals & Success Metrics

| Goal | Success Metric |
| :--- | :--- |
| Rapid project setup | Generate full docs in < 1 second |
| AI-ready documentation | Every doc includes agent-specific instructions |
| Tech stack alignment | Docs reflect actual Next.js patterns |

---

## 🧩 Functional Requirements

### Must Have
- [ ] Interactive project scaffolding via CLI prompts
- [ ] Auto-detection of project configuration from source
- [ ] Preset-based generation for common stacks
- [ ] AI-powered content enhancement

### Nice to Have
- [ ] Plugin system for custom generators
- [ ] Multi-language template support
- [ ] CI/CD integration templates

---

## 🔒 Non-Functional Requirements

- **Performance**: Docs generation under 2 seconds
- **Reliability**: Zero data loss on overwrites (backup system)
- **Compatibility**: Works with Node 18+ and all major package managers


